"title": "4846: shadow",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4846",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Primarily a symbol of protection, of the brevity of life and of the experience of death, in contrast to God's character and work.</p>\n<h2>Shadow as a general symbol of protection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:2-Isa30:3\">ISA 30:2–30:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:15\">JDG 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:45\">JER 48:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:7\">HOS 14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:5-Jonah4:6\">JON 4:5–4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:32\">MRK 4:32</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of God's protection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:1\">PSA 91:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">PSA 17:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:7\">PSA 36:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:7\">PSA 63:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:5\">PSA 121:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa4:5-Isa4:6\">ISA 4:5–4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4-Isa25:5\">ISA 25:4–25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:2\">ISA 49:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:16\">ISA 51:16</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of the protection given by God's chosen one</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:2\">ISA 32:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:20\">LAM 4:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:22-Ezek17:23\">EZK 17:22–17:23</a></p>\n<h2>Shadow as a symbol of life</h2>\n<h3>Of the brevity of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:4\">PSA 144:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:15\">1CH 29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:9\">JOB 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:2\">JOB 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:11\">PSA 102:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps109:23\">PSA 109:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:12\">ECC 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:13\">ECC 8:13</a></p>\n<h3>Of life's sadness and despair</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:9\">ISA 59:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:3-Job3:5\">JOB 3:3–3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:2-Job7:3\">JOB 7:2–7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:16\">JOB 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:7\">JOB 17:7</a></p>\n<h2>Shadow as a symbol of the experience of death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:17\">JOB 38:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:21-Job10:22\">JOB 10:21–10:22</a></p>\n<h2>Shadow in contrast to God</h2>\n<h3>Shadow contrasts with God's unchanging nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God's light pierces all shadow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:22\">JOB 12:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:22\">JOB 34:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:11-Ps139:12\">PSA 139:11–139:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:22\">DAN 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>God's salvation reaches to those whose life is in shadow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:16\">MAT 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2\">ISA 9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:1-Isa60:2\">ISA 60:1–60:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:79\">LUK 1:79</a></p>\n<h2>OT ceremonies as a shadow of the reality in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:16-Col2:17\">COL 2:16–2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:5\">HEB 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1\">HEB 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Real shadows</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:36\">JDG 9:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:19\">NEH 13:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:17\">SNG 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:6\">SNG 4:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:4\">JER 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>Real shadows invovled in miracles</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:9-2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:9–20:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:8\">ISA 38:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:15\">ACT 5:15</a></p>",
